title: DDFP: Don Draper gets the boot

description:
The NFL season is finally here and Dave and Rank could not be more excited. Well at least Dave is excited, Rank is kind of a pill. The fellas also talk some college football before jetting off into the future to take a look at some of this weekend's games. Give it a whirl, won't you?
